					<img itemprop="image" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/ImageObject" alt="Instagram Updates Logo and Its Fans Lose It Once Again" src="https://assets.entrepreneur.com/content/16x9/822/20160513164207-instagram-new-logo.jpeg" rel="share" />

					
							
								
				
				
